&amp;Expires=1679721591&amp;ssig=uvECsiXMUb&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/d5l0K8lGlx084130MyGs01041200d27i0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679721591&amp;ssig=PoQ3v0w%2B2q&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4881372712730629&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
