            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#减肥的人患肺结核风险增加#】春季是结核病菌高发期。结核病潜伏期4～8周，多发于抵抗力低下的人群，包括：糖尿病、肿瘤、艾滋病患者，吸烟人群，低体重...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%82%A3%E8%82%BA%E7%BB%93%E6%A0%B8%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%82%A3%E8%82%BA%E7%BB%93%E6%A0%B8%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#减肥的人患肺结核风险增加#</span></a>】春季是结核病菌高发期。结核病潜伏期4～8周，多发于抵抗力低下的人群，包括：糖尿病、肿瘤、艾滋病患者，吸烟人群，低体重、尤其是减肥的患者等。医生提醒，出现连续咳嗽超两周、午后低热盗汗、痰中带血丝等症状，要尽早筛查！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%8E%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%93%E6%A0%B8%E7%97%85%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%8E%E4%BD%93%E9%87%8D%E7%BE%A4%E4%BD%93%E6%98%AF%E7%BB%93%E6%A0%B8%E7%97%85%E9%AB%98%E5%8D%B1%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#低体重群体是结核病高危人群#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4882729322610721" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hcamu0h795j62yo1o07wi02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/2bAkNw3Plx08471daaVO01041200zutk0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679721591&amp;ssig=4DzYAykhDU&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/meaasjBBlx08471cEsK401041200itqX0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679721591&amp