            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>别怕！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E8%80%B3%E5%BF%B5%E7%8F%A0%E8%8F%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E8%BE%83%E4%BD%8E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E8%80%B3%E5%BF%B5%E7%8F%A0%E8%8F%8C%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E8%BE%83%E4%BD%8E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康人群感染耳念珠菌风险较低#</span></a> 】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%80%B3%E5%BF%B5%E7%8F%A0%E8%8F%8C%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%89%B9%E6%95%88%E8%8D%AF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%80%B3%E5%BF%B5%E7%8F%A0%E8%8F%8C%E7%9B%AE%E5%89%8D%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%89%B9%E6%95%88%E8%8D%AF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#耳念珠菌目前没有特效药#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%80%B3%E5%BF%B5%E7%8F%A0%E8%8F%8C%E5%B7%B2%E9%81%8D%E5%B8%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%9E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%80%B3%E5%BF%B5%E7%8F%A0%E8%8F%8C%E5%B7%B2%E9%81%8D%E5%B8%83%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%B8%80%E5%8D%8A%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%9E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#耳念珠菌已遍布美国一半以上的州#</span></a> 据美国疾控中心介绍，耳念珠菌主要威胁群体是免疫系统较弱的老年人，具有高传染性，并且对常见的抗真菌药物具备耐药性，容易在医院和老人护理机构传播，可导致重症患者死亡。目前缺少特效的治疗药物。美国最早于2016年发现第一例确诊病例。据报道，目前全美有三分之一感染者因为这种真菌死亡。<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4882479262400586" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/003z5L7fly8hc9u3yuzs6j60zk0k00vq02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/E5oOSv5Ilx0845UV0EM001041200BBeX0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679721591&amp;ssig=2LpJgs71bo&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/sif57KFllx0845UUbvfy01041200jJoI0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679721591&amp;ssig=2vrG%2Bt2ae9&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/gEfLIBgAlx0845UTUwSI01041200cLo50E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1679721591&amp;ssig=3W4y%2FIELup&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4882479262400586&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
